                                        Quy trình khám</h2>
                                </a>
                            </div>
                            <div class="metrouicss span3" style="background-color: #00A300; margin: 0 10px 5px 0;
                                height: 70px">
                                <a href="@Url.Action("DetailPage", "Home", new { ArticleID = "f7a915cc-9abf-4ba9-a702-06183ed1abb4" })">
